### ==========================================================================
### BildyApp API — DeliveryNote (Albarán) Endpoints
### ==========================================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@token = Bearer TU_ACCESS_TOKEN_AQUI

### ─── Crear un albarán de horas ──────────────────────────────────────────────
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/deliverynote
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "project": "SUSTITUIR_POR_PROJECT_ID",
  "client": "SUSTITUIR_POR_CLIENT_ID",
  "format": "hours",
  "description": "Jornada de electricidad — cableado planta 3",
  "workDate": "2026-04-20T08:00:00.000Z",
  "hours": 16,
  "workers": [
    { "name": "Juan García", "hours": 8 },
    { "name": "Pedro López", "hours": 8 }
  ]
}

###

### Crear un albarán de materiales
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/deliverynote
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "project": "SUSTITUIR_POR_PROJECT_ID",
  "client": "SUSTITUIR_POR_CLIENT_ID",
  "format": "material",
  "description": "Suministro de cemento y ladrillos",
  "workDate": "2026-04-21T09:00:00.000Z",
  "material": "Cemento Portland",
  "quantity": 50,
  "unit": "sacos"
}

###

### Listar albaranes (paginado + filtros)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/deliverynote?page=1&limit=10&sort=-workDate
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Filtrar por proyecto
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/deliverynote?project=SUSTITUIR_POR_PROJECT_ID
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Filtrar por formato y estado de firma
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/deliverynote?format=hours&signed=false
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Filtrar por rango de fechas
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/deliverynote?from=2026-04-01&to=2026-04-30
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Obtener un albarán por ID (con populate)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/deliverynote/SUSTITUIR_POR_ID
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Descargar PDF del albarán
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/deliverynote/pdf/SUSTITUIR_POR_ID
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Firmar un albarán (subir imagen de firma)
# NOTA: Para probar con VS Code REST Client,
# sustituir la ruta del archivo por una imagen real.
# Con curl: curl -X PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/deliverynote/ID/sign \
#   -H "Authorization: Bearer TOKEN" \
#   -F "signature=@/ruta/a/firma.png"
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/deliverynote/SUSTITUIR_POR_ID/sign
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----Boundary

------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="signature"; filename="firma.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./uploads/ejemplo-firma.png
------Boundary--

###

### Eliminar un albarán (solo si no está firmado)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/deliverynote/SUSTITUIR_POR_ID
Authorization: {{token}}
